 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f1112ecf22b7f8ad89daa967705dd2d1bb728b","tid":325732,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>段片幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好好睇 好有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6375fb917cd023ae4ecdfebae715d7684e3112a7","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打d片幾正～細個就已經覺得古生物好Q型</blockquote><br />\n多謝！<br />\n我相信好多男仔細個都曾經迷過古生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb7daeeeb22e663284eeb4eefd278dd0cc54da5","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條片唔錯，睇哂，期待下集</blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e23ec71cd8cff83354f9c6b49b606f6d5747cdf","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想知多d巨型烏賊既野 網上面個d全部一式一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n召喚傍觀巴打<br />\n我都𠯆大緊我個朋友蒲頭解答大家既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2fed097c594ddc2f6ca55fa7e51a59ad22af381","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:00:22.000Z","msg":"文字版本<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/Hydrarchos.jpg/250px-Hydrarchos.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ff7%2FHydrarchos.jpg%2F250px-Hydrarchos.jpg&d=sCocSN2yEkpdpwFnpEc9JTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=6604e33a\" target=\"_blank\">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/Hydrarchos.jpg/250px-Hydrarchos.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n1845年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來，主辦人既奸計被人揭發左：原來副骨只係求求其其用一堆不明來歷既化石砌出黎，用黎做展覽呃錢。主辦人當然即刻走佬啦。而有關「大海蛇」既傳聞亦逐漸被人淡忘。<br />\n<br />\n但係大家唔記得左一樣野，究竟堆來歷不明既化石係屬於咩生物既呢?"},{"pid":"3e31a662df46ade5de4121aa7669fa181f4bd541","tid":325732,"uid":114455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打d片幾正～細個就已經覺得古生物好Q型</blockquote><br />\n多謝！<br />\n我相信好多男仔細個都曾經迷過古生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望巴打快d出下一集"},{"pid":"2f21ef7262b9ba0f640f7c438032209a38227546","tid":325732,"uid":88072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:56:33.000Z","msg":"支持你"},{"pid":"41f21b97ce6b6cf1eca9ec9cf019b4740e2a815c","tid":325732,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>古生物真係痴撚線<br />\n咩鯊魚鱷魚都大過而家果D幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係有原因的!<br />\n但我唔肯定，交俾專業人仕解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似關大氣含氧量事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n昆蟲大細就關大氣含氧量事，其他就唔太關，你睇藍鯨唔單止係現今最大既動物，都係已知有史以來最大既動物"},{"pid":"dffae324802599cf6d5fb44d34a2638ee5d7bc95","tid":325732,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>古生物真係痴撚線<br />\n咩鯊魚鱷魚都大過而家果D幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係有原因的!<br />\n但我唔肯定，交俾專業人仕解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似關大氣含氧量事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n昆蟲關事既原因係因為呼吸方式，昆蟲主要用氣孔呼吸，空氣直接由體外氣孔入體內再去身體各部分，如果氧含量低，咁氧氣擴散既速度都會慢，什至唔夠(濃度差異會影響擴散速度)，所以氧含量低既環境，昆蟲氣孔距離同身體最入既距離唔可以太遠，所以就限制左體形。<br />\n而大約3億x年前左右(石炭紀)，氧濃度大約40%，即係依加既兩倍，所以昆蟲可以更大隻。"},{"pid":"e2149eaf8a05ed80a6853b8ef9198d27edacf51e","tid":325732,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bf3e2cd193545defa2f2f395cdef8390b9a942","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>古生物真係痴撚線<br />\n咩鯊魚鱷魚都大過而家果D幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係有原因的!<br />\n但我唔肯定，交俾專業人仕解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似關大氣含氧量事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n昆蟲大細就關大氣含氧量事，其他就唔太關，你睇藍鯨唔單止係現今最大既動物，都係已知有史以來最大既動物</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正呀巴打"},{"pid":"98c61c40f66cd9ff6f46c4b13d10bfbc52c1bfb2","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"貼埋剩低個啲先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Owen-Basilosaurus-vertebra.JPEG/220px-Owen-Basilosaurus-vertebra.JPEG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F4%2F4e%2FOwen-Basilosaurus-vertebra.JPEG%2F220px-Owen-Basilosaurus-vertebra.JPEG&h=fdf9a797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事實上，堆化石早係1834年，已經有科學家研究過。當時佢地認為呢副骨屬於一條海中既大蜥蝪。<br />\n<br />\n所以被當時就俾左個好有霸氣既名俾佢，Basliosaurous，<span style=\"color: red;\">「帝王龍」</span>！但係隨住科學家挖掘出肋骨同其餘部分既化石，發現佢並唔係咩蜥蝪，而係一種古代既鯨類。所以佢就被改名成為「龍王鯨」啦，但係英文名都依然係Basliosaurous 既。<br />\n<br />\n龍王鯨生活係3400萬年前既海域入面，算係現代鯨魚既祖先之一。生到又長又粗，當然係個陣海入面既霸者之一啦。個頭雖然細但牙尖嘴利，海入面既動物基本上都係佢既獵物。黎番現代，佢既後裔都繼續係海中霸者。有Ｄ，都依然繼續靠尖牙利齒搵食既。但係有D呢，排牙就演化到好似梳咁，用黎隔住海水入面既浮游生物，然後再一下子吞落肚，實行密食當三番呀。例如鬚鯨咁，就有一排好似梳咁既牙啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://kids.coa.gov.tw/upload/images/knowledge/coa_taita_20081106110008/10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkids.coa.gov.tw%2Fupload%2Fimages%2Fknowledge%2Fcoa_taita_20081106110008%2F10.jpg&h=ad356667&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e2f65e84defac36065b9b6c6fc6050aed3453c5","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>古生物真係痴撚線<br />\n咩鯊魚鱷魚都大過而家果D幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係有原因的!<br />\n但我唔肯定，交俾專業人仕解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似關大氣含氧量事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n昆蟲關事既原因係因為呼吸方式，昆蟲主要用氣孔呼吸，空氣直接由體外氣孔入體內再去身體各部分，如果氧含量低，咁氧氣擴散既速度都會慢，什至唔夠(濃度差異會影響擴散速度)，所以氧含量低既環境，昆蟲氣孔距離同身體最入既距離唔可以太遠，所以就限制左體形。<br />\n而大約3億x年前左右(石炭紀)，氧濃度大約40%，即係依加既兩倍，所以昆蟲可以更大隻。</blockquote><br />\n其實以我所知，海入面生物既大細係冇咩受到年代有好大變遷既<br />\n但係陸地同空既生物就史前既生物普遍大過現代？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d77d890e3028c429bb9d3ea1dbfc461ff7c2ab","tid":325732,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:47:59.000Z","msg":"斷好<br />\n快啲up多啲片"},{"pid":"8c66616b4280ca7732f7a54e4433de0814362bac","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"但係要論長粗大（同埋黑）啦喎，龍王鯨就比起佢啲後裔稍為遜色啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img0.dili360.com/rw9/ga/M00/3F/0F/wKgBy1Z3y1qAdWbsAAvKJ7NC0N8449.tub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg0.dili360.com%2Frw9%2Fga%2FM00%2F3F%2F0F%2FwKgBy1Z3y1qAdWbsAAvKJ7NC0N8449.tub.jpg&h=042671eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢既其中一隻後代，世上最大既動物藍鯨，可以生到身長超過三十米，重二百噸。即係仲長過三架香港巴士連住，重過四十隻大象加埋。<br />\n<br />\n比起上黎，龍王鯨身型咁纖瘦，身長亦都大約得１８米。講得好聽D似海怪，難聽D似鰻魚多過鯨魚。隻鰭又細，游水要好似條蛇咁游，正一軟皮蛇"},{"pid":"b7d3dd1e47a51d1f3c1959b3d40189198977fb34","tid":325732,"uid":47647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:52:37.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0b6179f4f493f3f4da4d1c78e6e27d8d2c6b30c8","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:55:13.000Z","msg":"講到佢咁渣咁，其實帝王龍都有一個特徵，係佢有，現代鯨類冇既。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1153/d1153523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1153%2Fd1153523.jpg&h=5a2dc6aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係隻後腳仔啦！。隻腳雖然得一米長，對於一隻十幾廿米既生物黎講，其實幾多餘。有啲科學家什至懷疑，話呢隻後腳只可以係佢地敦倫其間輔助下。而呢對多餘既後腳，什至係佢地既後裔－鯨魚身上，直情消失埋。呢個情況其實類似人既尾龍骨咁，係演化既過程入面係非常常見既。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鯨魚特別既地方，在於佢係唯一一種哺乳類動物，係完全適應係海入面既生活架。睇到龍王鯨呢隻腳仔，又令我諗起細細個睇Discovery channel 既時候諗起既問題：鯨魚既祖先係點樣由陸地下海，成為一條魚架呢？"},{"pid":"ff8544819f19a53413df29fcfeefe9dae4ed4fee","tid":325732,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:55:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fc07dd936ad57d64cedac41f168634650be0248","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.uua.cn/uploadfile/2014/0304/20140304064316839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.uua.cn%2Fuploadfile%2F2014%2F0304%2F20140304064316839.jpg&h=dd948095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來果然發現到係龍王鯨出現冇幾耐之前（大約幾千萬年咁啦），有隻怪獸EXACT7LY，係隻識行識走識游水既「鯨魚」。<br />\n<br />\n佢叫步行鯨，雖然個樣似鱷魚多過似鯨魚，不過佢既耳骨構造同鯨類有一樣既特徵，從而得知佢地係鯨魚既祖祖先。<br />\n<br />\n步行鯨四隻腳明顯短但係粗壯，係陸地上面就唔係咁靈活。但係學鱷魚潛水做STALKER，都幾專業架。<br />\n<br />\n而且佢地腳掌好闊，好似著左對蛙鞋咁，離鯨魚下海既日子已經唔遠了。"},{"pid":"0dcfb84b4dad0535bddc3beb06bbb1c8b8e8d76e","tid":325732,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實俾鯨魚食左係咪真係有機會唔死?"},{"pid":"a69bd4eee4009d505ddb0482397c74d3c1ab983b","tid":325732,"uid":63152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:04:25.000Z","msg":"係街睇片好食流量<br />\n好彩有文字版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f23b8e8008e9753aa67d1a702815a52299f89f3","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:05:32.000Z","msg":"咁即係鯨魚一開始已經係好似步行鯨咁水陸兩用，然後再變成而家好似魚咁既様? <br />\n<br />\n當然唔係啦，更古老既鯨完全係係陸地生活架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.big5.enorth.com.cn/0/05/80/06/5800697_805574.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.big5.enorth.com.cn%2F0%2F05%2F80%2F06%2F5800697_805574.jpg&h=c64e867a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而佢地個樣係咁既，成隻黃鼠狼咁<br />\n<br />\n相比步行鯨，佢有直立同強壯既四肢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.nyit.edu/files/medicine/cetacean_family_tree_pakicetus_spp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nyit.edu%2Ffiles%2Fmedicine%2Fcetacean_family_tree_pakicetus_spp.jpg&h=557edc6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間唔中會落下水咁啦。<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢個鼻窿係嘴尖，相反現代鯨類鼻窿就係頭頂；雖然佢同現代鯨類個樣完全唔似．但係憑住佢既耳骨，我地知道原來佢就係鯨類既祖祖祖先啦。<br />\n<br />\n就係咁，龍王鯨呢隻海怪既起源之謎可謂已經解開。"},{"pid":"29d2aad1e0e6e13ecb34315f6dd70eb558d31bcc","tid":325732,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e89f9895b785a47dd0fc2d4755d361031a6ac88a","tid":325732,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢類形嘅片平時睇D鬼佬講得好快<br />\n你講得慢唔係好慣<br />\n不過聽得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講太快我自己錄都錄得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋最緊要大家聽得舒服姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細佬我有個朋友話你朋友條片幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1607b3a70ab4562c25f41f4873cdfcaa760ff0","tid":325732,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"最後比大家估下除左鯨類之外，當今世上同龍王鯨關係最近既動物係咩? <br />\nTips: 佢係哺乳類動物，有蹄又識潛水<br />\n<br />\n答案係:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n河馬<br />\n<br />\n[img<a href=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/wwfeatures/wm/live/624_351/images/live/p0/3d/tk/p03dtkw2.jpg[/]img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fwwfeatures%2Fwm%2Flive%2F624_351%2Fimages%2Flive%2Fp0%2F3d%2Ftk%2Fp03dtkw2.jpg%5B%2F%5Dimg%5D&d=sCocSN2yEkpdpwFnpEc9JTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=9358419b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/wwfeatures/wm/live/624_351/images/live/p0/3d/tk/p03dtkw2.jpg[/]img]</a>"}]}